1
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,439
If the Imperial Inspectorate stops my work,

2
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,519
then His Majesty's favor would be wasted.

3
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:32,680
No, no.

4
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,000
I need to find another way.

5
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:44,640
Halt!

6
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,519
Stop right there!

7
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,159
We're from the Capital Prefecture.

8
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,760
Thank you, sir, for your help.

9
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:52,879
Chasing him down the street...

10
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,159
What crime did he commit?

11
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:54,920
Theft.

12
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:55,920
I...

13
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,159
I didn't steal anything.

14
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:59,040
I came to file a complaint.

15
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,560
I've been wrongly accused!

16
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,159
Shut your mouth!

17
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,519
One more word out of you,

18
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:03,599
and you'll be killed on sight.

19
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:04,359
Hold on.

20
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:06,200
The Imperial Inspectorate is on the case.

21
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,479
Lower your blade.

22
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:11,919
My lord,

23
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,680
this is a Capital Prefecture matter.

24
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,400
What?

25
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,400
A Capital Prefecture case—

26
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,800
the Imperial Inspectorate can't intervene?

27
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,280
You cried injustice.

28
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,520
What happened?

29
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,639
Can you take charge of this?

30
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:31,159
The Imperial Inspectorate oversees all,

31
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,800
granted by His Majesty himself,

32
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,240
with imperial authority.

33
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,039
So tell me, can I take charge?

34
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:38,639
My lord,

35
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,240
I'm a commoner from Zhenyuan County, Zhenzhou.

36
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,599
I accuse the magistrate, Ai Wenguang.

37
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,319
He fabricates charges and imprisons the innocent,

38
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,599
seizes property by force,

39
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:49,520
and treats lives as worthless, my lord!

40
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,520
The people of Zhenyuan County

41
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:53,560
have no way to survive!

42
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,360
I beg you, my lord, deliver us justice!

43
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,319
Silence!

44
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,840
How dare you!

45
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,759
Harming a commoner before the Imperial Inspectorate?

46
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:01,919
My lord,

47
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,520
perhaps you needn't trouble yourself with this.

48
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,240
Zhenyuan County belongs to Chongzhou Prefecture,

49
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:09,280
the Left Chancellor's fief.

50
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,560
The Left Chancellor?

51
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,280
The Imperial Inspectorate oversees all.

52
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:17,039
Who the hell is the Left Chancellor?

53
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:22,960
My lord,

54
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,560
I carry a petition signed by thousands.

55
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:30,639
Please, save the people of Zhenyuan County!

56
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:46,960
What are you standing there for?

57
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:47,919
Take him away, now.

58
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,479
My lord,

59
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,280
this is a Capital Prefecture case.

60
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,199
What you're doing breaks the rules.

61
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:55,840
Rules?

62
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,639
All of you, listen up.

63
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:02,680
The Imperial Inspectorate takes this case.

64
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,199
Anyone who dares resist

65
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:07,520
will stand trial at the Imperial Inspectorate.

66
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,560
My lord,

67
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,759
is this really necessary?

68
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:14,000
The Capital Prefecture is truly capable.

69
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,759
Right under the Emperor's nose,

70
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,040
a case like this—

71
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,800
you turned it into a theft charge.

72
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:22,560
Crawl back and tell your prefect:

73
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,639
when I find the time,

74
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:27,199
I'll be paying him a visit.

75
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:39,279
Thank you, my lord.

76
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:45,000
Eat slowly.

77
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:45,800
Don't choke.

78
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,560
Are you the only one from Zhenyuan County?

79
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:51,839
In answer to my lord,

80
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,759
there were over a dozen of us originally.

81
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,639
But we were hunted down all the way.

82
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,560
By the time we reached the capital,

83
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,199
only four or five remained.

84
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:06,240
The rest were seized by officials days ago.

85
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,959
Officials shielding each other,

86
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,439
all in collusion.

87
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,279
This isn't just about the Zhenyuan magistrate.

88
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:14,480
The whole bureaucracy is rotten to the core.

89
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,439
My lord,

90
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,560
do we still have any hope of surviving?

91
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,600
Rest assured.

92
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,199
With me here,

93
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,600
I will surely win you justice.

94
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,759
Thank you, my lord.

95
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,639
Please rise.

96
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,279
Seeing injustice, I must intervene.

97
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,160
Don't kneel before me again.

98
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,480
You and I are no different.

99
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,079
Young master,

100
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:43,439
you're really something.

101
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,399
The case is solved.

102
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,800
Exactly as you predicted.

103
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,639
Illicit affairs always lead to murder,

104
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:50,439
sordid feuds within noble households.

105
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:51,600
It's always the same pattern.

106
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,439
Young Master Ning,

107
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,800
let's just speak frankly here.

108
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:56,759
You're a young master from a noble house.

109
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,600
Coming to the Imperial Inspectorate

110
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,959
is just to gild your credentials.

111
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:01,759
But don't worry.

112
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:02,439
This time,

113
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,920
we'll state clearly in the records

114
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,120
that you assisted with the case.

115
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:09,319
That bit of trifling credit, though,

116
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:10,600
just leave it to us.

117
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:14,000
No wonder you've been cold to me.

118
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,319
You feared I'd steal the credit.

119
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,519
We're all brothers from now on.

120
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,800
On this case, I merely

121
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,279
provided a small clue or two.

122
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,720
How could I dare claim credit?

123
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,399
I'm not Feng Qizheng, after all.

124
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,000
Case solved, top credit goes to you.

125
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,040
When the reward comes through,

126
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,800
you take the lion's share.

127
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,920
Feng Qizheng? No way.

128
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,240
Hold on,

129
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,279
that man is selfish to the core,

130
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:31,879
never thinks of others...

131
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,000
Old Gao, what did you just say about me?

132
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,040
You called me selfish?

133
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,519
How dare you, Old Gao!

134
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:35,279
All right, all right, enough.

135
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:37,240
You two brothers, this time,

136
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,759
have toiled and worried day and night.

137
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,639
The top credit

138
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:42,000
rightfully belongs to you.

139
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,920
Oh, how could we possibly accept that?

140
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,480
Listen to Old Gao here.

141
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:57,000
As if we'd steal someone's credit.

142
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:00,439
We at the Imperial Inspectorate

143
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,680
always enforce the law impartially.

144
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:04,319
Credit goes where credit's due.

145
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:05,560
Lord Ning.

146
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,160
Ning Chen.

147
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,839
I underestimated you before.

148
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,839
Didn't expect you'd have real skill.

149
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:15,439
Feng Qizheng apologizes for his earlier attitude.

150
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,600
Brother Feng, you're too kind.

151
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:20,720
I have much to learn from you two.

152
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:21,920
How about this.

153
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,079
Once the reward money comes in,

154
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:25,560
I'll treat you brothers to food and drinks.

155
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,839
Now you're talking.

156
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:31,879
Brother.

157
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,480
Skip the meal.

158
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,439
True enough.

159
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,720
We've got to hit the Pleasure Quarter!

160
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,079
The girls there are truly stunning.

161
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,000
Listen, Old Gao.

162
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,120
Pleasure Quarter, Pleasure Quarter.

163
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,920
Is that all you ever think about?

164
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:50,519
Look at Ning Chen.

165
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,600
He's surely

166
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,800
a virgin, you know.

167
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,959
Still a virgin.

168
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,800
Aren't you going to lead him astray?

169
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:57,639
Just look at you.

170
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,040
This...

171
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:01,040
Brother.

172
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:01,920
Brother.

173
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,319
Don't be nervous.

174
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,399
Brother Gao here is a man of passion.

175
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:07,519
Bold and straightforward.

176
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,879
When he says "Pleasure Quarter,"

177
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,000
he means investigating a case.

178
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:11,079
Investigating, yeah.

179
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:12,120
Come on, out with you.

180
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,920
What are you lot sneaking about for?

181
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,000
Nothing at all.

182
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,639
Ning Chen, come with me.

183
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:42,639
Wait, Ning Chen.

184
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,799
What did you do wrong?

185
00:08:44,919 --> 00:08:46,240
Why is Golden Guard Pan's face

186
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,759
even uglier than when he smiles?

187
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,159
He looks ugly either way.

188
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:52,240
Ning Chen.

189
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,720
Old Pan's cold-faced but warm-hearted.

190
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,840
Tell you what, you go ahead.

191
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,759
We'll handle things here.

192
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:56,320
Right.

193
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,360
Alright.

194
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,639
Then this brother here,

195
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,200
I'll trust you to look after him well.

196
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:00,840
Don't worry.

197
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,759
My lords.

198
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,600
I didn't hear. I didn't hear.

199
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:14,759
Didn't hear a thing.

200
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,039
I really didn't hear anything.

201
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,000
Lord Pan.

202
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:26,879
Ning Chen.

203
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:28,840
Do you know your offense?

204
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,120
What did I do?

205
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,080
Grabbing a man from the Capital Prefecture.

206
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,080
Making enemies for no reason.

207
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,840
Getting Commander Geng impeached.

208
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,840
And reprimanded by His Majesty.

209
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:38,679
You did nothing wrong?

210
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:42,600
The Imperial Inspectorate's main duty is oversight.

211
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:43,799
Handling cases is only secondary.

212
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:46,480
Cases beyond the Capital Prefecture go to the Three Courts.

213
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,759
Cases beyond the Three Courts

214
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:49,320
are passed to the Imperial Inspectorate.

215
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,080
Golden Guard Pan.

216
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,559
Do you always rush to judgment

217
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,639
and scold subordinates without hearing them out?

218
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:55,840
How dare you!

219
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,879
You dare talk back to me?

220
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:59,120
Not only am I talking back,

221
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,840
I'm also questioning your competence.

222
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,200
Who gave you the nerve to question me?

223
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,399
Liang Jingru did.

224
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:08,519
Who is Liang Jingru?

225
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:09,639
The one who gave me courage.

226
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:12,600
Ning Chen.

227
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:16,039
I'll set aside this Liang Jingru for now.

228
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:18,440
But taking a man from the Capital Prefecture

229
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,399
violates the rules.

230
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,360
Send him back at once.

231
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,919
And if I refuse?

232
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,840
I'm not asking you.

233
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,480
I'm ordering you.

234
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:35,679
Cheeky brat.

235
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,639
He really is something different.

236
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:42,799
Chen.

237
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:44,679
Where are you storming off to?

238
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,759
What did Golden Guard Pan say?

239
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:47,679
Nothing at all.

240
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:48,960
By the way,

241
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,159
do you know where Commander Geng is?

242
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,480
I've been here so long

243
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,720
and still haven't met our chief.

244
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,480
Commander Geng?

245
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:56,080
The Imperial Inspectorate command post.

246
00:10:58,799 --> 00:10:59,240
Got it.

247
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:01,080
Look after Li Si for me.

248
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:03,480
I'll treat you to the Pleasure Quarter.

249
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,720
We'll take good care of him.

250
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:14,519
Imperial Inspectorate Silver Guard Ning Chen greets Commander Geng.

251
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,159
What is it?

252
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,480
I have something here.

253
00:11:23,639 --> 00:11:24,759
Please take a look, Commander.

254
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:35,559
A petition signed in blood.

255
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,519
Where did this come from?

256
00:11:38,039 --> 00:11:40,519
Zhenyuan County folk came to file an imperial appeal,

257
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:41,720
but the Capital Prefecture's men

258
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,919
twisted it into a theft case.

259
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:45,320
I seized this from their hands.

260
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,120
Commander Geng.

261
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,879
The people of Zhenyuan County

262
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,320
would never have risked their lives

263
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,840
to come petition the Emperor

264
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,200
unless they were truly desperate.

265
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:55,440
Had I not come across this today,

266
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,559
the truth about Zhenyuan County

267
00:11:56,879 --> 00:11:58,080
would never have come to light.

268
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,080
The Ministry of Justice and Capital Prefecture

269
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,360
can handle this.

270
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:07,799
Commander Geng.

271
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:10,639
I volunteer to go to Zhenyuan and uncover the truth.

272
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,360
Does Golden Guard Pan know?

273
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,159
He doesn't.

274
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:14,200
And he doesn't need to know.

275
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:17,120
Bypassing the chain of command: thirty lashes.

276
00:12:17,759 --> 00:12:18,679
Wait till I return from this case,

277
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:19,840
and I'll take three hundred.

278
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:22,879
Did I say you could go?

279
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,399
Commander Geng.

280
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,399
What is this supposed to mean?

281
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:35,080
The Imperial Inspectorate answers to me.

282
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,440
Don't think His Majesty's favor

283
00:12:37,559 --> 00:12:38,919
puts you above the law.

